<paragraph>MyRDSInstance:</paragraph>
<paragraph>Tipo: 'AWS::RDS::DBInstance' Propriedades:</paragraph>
<paragraph>DBName: MyRDSInstance</paragraph>
<paragraph>AllocatedStorage: '20' DBInstanceClass: db.t2.micro</paragraph>
<paragraph>Motor: mysql</paragraph>
